FBIS4-38724 "drsov106_b_94010" FBIS-SOV-94-106 Daily Report 1 Jun 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues Reponsibility for Reform To Be Shared With Regions Reponsibility for Reform To Be Shared With Regions LD0106114494 Moscow Russian Television Network in Russian 0400 GMT 1 Jun 94 LD0106114494 Moscow Russian Television Network Russian BFN [From the "Vesti" newscast] [Text] The end of check privatization will give the government the opportunity to depart fully from the present economically fruitless tactic of denationalization. At a recent meeting between [Prime Minister] Viktor Chernomyrdin and the heads of regional administrations, it was said that the government intends to share responsibility for changing the tactics of reform with regions which have not yet even defined their attitude to it.
